race.comment: Happy to throw up DEEL HER IN (8) as she steps out to 1500m once again. She looked a very progressive type when winning a Listed race at this track and trip in February but has been around 1200m this time in work. Things looks ideal here with a good draw on offer and she can return to her best form. CAMERA ACTION (5) finished off strongly after settling last in the run over 1400m last time out. ZJP rides now and the 3kg claim sees her carry no weight. Her third-up record is very impressive and with further improvement in store, she'll be hard to hold out. SOLDANELLE (3) got the job done after sitting midfield over the mile here 35 days ago. Pike remains in the saddle and her coming into this on the fresh side looks a good move, judging by her fresh record. May get back in the run but watch for her late. BOLD HERO (4) can improve on the fresh performance and is not out of this. RAPID ROCK (12) is next best out in trip for the first time.
